(1, 1, '2015-07-12 14:30:57', '2015-07-12 14:30:57', '<div class="preview-body-holder removable-parent order-handle">\r\n<div id="vbid-04f3d-sltrbzqgwe" class="preview-element preview-body magic-circle-holder text-element quick-text-style-menu" data-menu-name="PREVIEW_BODY">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/my_SM-T116NDWUXME_000000001_Front_white?$DT-Gallery$" alt="" width="900" height="600" />\r\n\r\nSamsung India recently introduced the Galaxy Tab 3 V. It launched the Galaxy Tab A (With support for both FDD LTE Band 3 and TDD LTE Band 40) and Galaxy Tab E (3G) voice-calling tablets last month.Samsung''s new tablet is now listed on the company''s India e-store priced at Rs. 10,600. As of writing, its not available but is expected to go on sale very soon.\r\n\r\nThe specifications of the device are as following:-\r\n\r\n*Android 4.4 KitKat (Touchwiz)\r\n\r\n*7-inch WSVGA (1024x600 pixels) LCD display with a 16:9 screen ratio\r\n\r\n*3G (Voice call not supported)\r\n\r\n*1.3GHz quad-core processor\r\n\r\n*1GB RAM\r\n\r\n*8GB In-built storage (Expandable upto 32GB)\r\n\r\n*5-megapixel rear camera\r\n\r\n*Dimensions- 193.4x116.4x9.7mm and w\r\n\r\neighs 322 grams\r\n\r\n*3600mAh battery\r\n\r\n*Wi-Fi, GPS, Glonass, Bluetooth 4.0, and Micro-USB\r\n\r\n(Image source- http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/my_SM-T116NDWUXME_000000001_Front_white?$DT-Gallery$)\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 V', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2015-07-12 18:23:28', '2015-07-12 18:23:28', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(253, 1, '2015-09-02 00:32:53', '2015-09-01 19:02:53', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Gionee-F103.jpg" alt="" width="684" height="800" />\r\n\r\nGionee yesterday launched its new smartphone "F103" in India. It has been priced at Rs. 9,999 and supports 4G. It supports a glass back panel and a metal body. It will be available in Pearl White, Dawn White and Black colors. Its specifications are as following:-\r\n\r\n*Android 5.0 Lollipop (Amigo 3.0 UI)\r\n\r\n*5-Inch HD (720x1280 pixels) IPS display\r\n\r\n*64-Bit 1.3GHz quad-core MediaTek MT6735 processor\r\n\r\n*2GB RAM\r\n\r\n*16GB In-built storage (Expandable upto 32GB)\r\n\r\n*8MP Rear camera and a 5MP front camera\r\n\r\n*Wi-Fi, GPS/ A-GPS, GPRS/ EDGE, 4G, Bluetooth and Micro-USB\r\n\r\n*2400mAh Battery\r\n\r\n*Dimensions:146x70.3x7.95mm\r\n\r\nAccording to Timir Baran Acharyya (GM, Gionee India), "With our F series we have achieved to get both design and performance in one device and consumers gets the best from both the worlds. F103 is a power packed device a great design which not only gives great performance but also adds the style quotient to the consumer who carries it out."\r\n\r\n(Image source- http://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Gionee-F103.jpg)', 'Gionee F103', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gionee-f103', '', '', '2015-09-02 00:34:57', '2015-09-01 19:04:57', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=253', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(240, 1, '2015-08-23 20:24:09', '2015-08-23 14:54:09', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://ina-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/huawei.jpeg" alt="" width="635" height="476" />\r\n\r\nHuawei recently launched its new smartphone "Honor 7i".  It has been priced at CNY 1,599 (Rs. 16,500) for the 2GB RAM and 16GB variant and CNY 1,899 (Rs. 19,500) for the 3GB RAM and 32GB variant. It comes with a fingerprint scanner and a rotatable camera which allows the same camera to act as the rear as well as the front camera. Its specifications are as following:-\r\n\r\n*Android 5.1 Lollipop (Emotion UI 3.1)\r\n\r\n*5.2-Inch HD (1080x1920 pixels) IPS display\r\n\r\n*1.5Ghz+1.2Ghz 64-Bit octa-core Snapdragon 616 processor\r\n\r\n*Adreno 405 GPU\r\n\r\n*13MP Rotatable camera\r\n\r\n*Bluetooth, GPS/ A-GPS, 3G, 4G LTE, Wi-Fi and Micro-USB\r\n\r\n*3100mAh Battery\r\n\r\n*Dimensions: 141.6x71.2x7.8mm  and weighs 160g\r\n\r\n(Image source- http://cdn.gsmarena.com/vv/newsimg/15/04/huawei-honor-7-leaked/gsmarena_001.jpg\r\n\r\nhttp://ina-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/huawei.jpeg)\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone" src="http://cdn.gsmarena.com/vv/newsimg/15/04/huawei-honor-7-leaked/gsmarena_001.jpg" alt="" width="590" height="325" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Huawei Honor 7i', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'huawei-honor-7i', '', '', '2015-08-23 20:24:09', '2015-08-23 14:54:09', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=240', 0, 'post', '', 0),
