(27, 1, '2015-07-12 17:25:16', '2015-07-12 17:25:16', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://news.highonandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/07/xiaomi-mi5-1.png" alt="" width="829" height="459" />\r\n<div class="preview-body-holder removable-parent order-handle">\r\n<div id="vbid-08699-sltrbzqgwe" class="preview-element preview-body magic-circle-holder text-element quick-text-style-menu" data-menu-name="PREVIEW_BODY">\r\n\r\nChinese Weibo recently leaked  Xiaomi''s upcoming  flagship device Mi5''s specifications and also hinted about a bigger variant of the Mi5 ie the Mi5 Plus.\r\n\r\nMi5:-\r\n\r\nThe device is said to have a 5.2-inch QHD (1440x2560 pixels) Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display. The Mi 5 is likely to be powered by a Snapdragon 810 processor . The device might come with a 16-megapixel rear camera alongside a large 13-megapixel sensor on the front. It might also come packed with a 3000 mAh battery.\r\n\r\nMi5 Plus:-\r\n\r\nThe Device is said to have a 5.7-inch QHD (1440x2560 pixels) Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display.The Mi5 Plus is likely to be powered by  a Snapdragon 820 processor, a 3500mAh battery, and the smartphone is said to charge from 0 to 100 percent in 50 minutes. The leaked details also hint that the Mi 5 Plus might come with a 23-megapixel rear camera with OIS and laser autofocus and a 12-megapixel front camera.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n(Image source- http://news.highonandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/07/xiaomi-mi5-1.png)', 'Xiaomi Mi5, Mi5 Plus''s leaked specs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'xiaomi-mi5-mi5-pluss-leaked-specs', '', '', '2015-07-12 18:22:57', '2015-07-12 18:22:57', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=27', 0, 'post', '', 0),
