(124, 1, '2015-07-19 12:00:08', '2015-07-19 06:30:08', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://www.sammobile.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Samsung-Galaxy-J7-01.jpg" alt="" width="782" height="499" />\r\n\r\nSamsung on Thursday launched its new 4G enabled devices Galaxy J5 and Galaxy J7 in India. Both are available exclusively on Flipkart to pre-order and will be delivered on 24th July priced at Rs.11,999 and Rs.14,999 respectively. Their specifications are as following:\r\n\r\nSamsung Galaxy J5\r\n\r\n* Android 5.1.1 (Lollipop) (Touchwiz UI)\r\n\r\n*5-Inch Super Amoled HD display\r\n\r\n*1.2GHz Quad-core Snapdragon 410\r\n\r\n*1.5GB RAM\r\n\r\n*3MP Rear camera (Autofocus) and a 5MP front camera\r\n\r\n*8GB In-built storage\r\n\r\n*2,600mAh Battery\r\n\r\n*Dimensions: 142 x 73 x 8.5 mm and weighs 149g\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en">\r\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en"><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/GalaxyJ5J7?src=hash">#GalaxyJ5J7</a> with 4G LTE for multi-player gaming! Pre-book on <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Flipkart?src=hash">#Flipkart</a>. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TheGameJustGotBigger?src=hash">#TheGameJustGotBigger</a><a href="http://t.co/uaxT0GxxkZ">http://t.co/uaxT0GxxkZ</a><a href="http://t.co/z6T7RGbjIU">pic.twitter.com/z6T7RGbjIU</a></p>\r\n— Samsung Mobile India (@SamsungMobileIN) <a href="https://twitter.com/SamsungMobileIN/status/622035525646594048">July 17, 2015</a></blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSamsung Galaxy J7\r\n\r\n*Android 5.1.1 (Lollipop) (Touchwiz UI)\r\n\r\n*5.5-Inch screen\r\n\r\n*1.5GHz Octa-core Exynos 7580\r\n\r\n*16GB In-Built storage (Expandable upto 128GB)\r\n\r\n*1.5 GB RAM\r\n\r\n*3,000mAh Battery\r\n\r\n*Dimensions: 152.2 x 79.1 x 7.9 mm and weighs 169g\r\n\r\n(Image source- http://www.reviews5stars.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Samsung-Galaxy-J1-932x542.jpg\r\n\r\nhttp://tpucdn.com/npu/img/2015/05-22/21193-45f1966e_945_556.jpg\r\n\r\nhttp://www.sammobile.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Sams