(139, 1, '2015-07-22 19:08:25', '2015-07-22 13:38:25', '<p><img class="alignnone" src="http://st1.bgr.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/xolo-black.jpg" alt="" width="827" height="456" /></p>\r\n<p>Xolo recently launched its new smartphone "Black" in India. Its body is made up of Polycarbonate and it also has Corning Gorilla Glass 3 on both of its sides. It has curvy edges and a matt finish. It has been priced at Rs. 12,999 and is exclusively available on Flipkart.  Its specifications are as following:-</p>\r\n<p>* Android 5.0.2 (Hive UI)</p>\r\n<p>*5.5-inch Full HD</p>\r\n<p>*1.5GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon 615</p>\r\n<p>*Adreno 405 GPU</p>\r\n<p>*2GB RAM</p>\r\n<p>*16GB In-built storage (Expandable upto 32GB)</p>\r\n<p>*13MP Primary camera and a 2MP secondary camera (Both with flash)</p>\r\n<p>*3,200mAh Battery</p>\r\n<p>*Dimensions: 155.5 x 76.6 x 7.3 mm</p>\r\n<p>*Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, hotspot, Bluetooth v4.0, 4G</p>\r\n<p>(Image source- http://deleteprice.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/xolo-black-mobile-phone-large-2.jpg</p>\r\n<p>http://st1.bgr.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/xolo-black.jpg</p>\r\n<p>http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/thumb/msid-47867406,width-217,resizemode-4/Xolo-Black.jpg)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class="alignnone" src="http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/thumb/msid-47867406,width-217,resizemode-4/Xolo-Black.jpg" alt="" width="217" height="163" /></p>\r\n<p><img class="alignnone" src="http://deleteprice.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/xolo-black-mobile-phone-large-2.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="400" /></p>\r\n', 'Xolo Black', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'xolo-black', '', '', '2015-07-22 19:08:25', '2015-07-22 13:38:25', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=139', 0, 'post', '', 0),
