(151, 1, '2015-07-24 14:00:36', '2015-07-24 08:30:36', '<img class="alignnone" src="https://lh6.ggpht.com/mp86vbELnqLi2FzvhiKdPX31_oiTRLNyeK8x4IIrbF5eD1D5RdnVwjQP0hwMNR_JdA=w300" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\r\n\r\nWhatsApp recently released a new update which has got some really cool features. The new updated version of WhatsApp is not currently available on Google Play Store but can be downloaded directly from its official website ie <a href="http://www.whatsapp.com">www.whatsapp.com</a>\r\n\r\nIts new features are as following:-\r\n\r\n*MARK AS UNREAD\r\n\r\nYes, you heard it right! now you have the power to mark any message as unread. But, before you get too excited, its not what you''re thinking about. This feature enables a user to highlight any important message as unread, which means that the same wouldn''t reflect on the other person''s phone.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*CUSTOM OPTIONS\r\n\r\nWhatsApp will now have a new set of options which will enable a user to set ringtone for a particular caller and you can also toggle the notifications, vibration and different notification lights for different contacts.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*MUTE CONTACT\r\n\r\nYou can also mute any contact by simply marking it in the about menu.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*LOWER DATA CONSUMPTION FOR CALLS\r\n\r\nYou can now enable low data consumption by marking the low data usage option under chats and calls menu in settings.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*GOOGLE DRIVE INTEGRATION\r\n\r\nNow, users will have an option to backup their chats on Google drive. This has been a much awaited feature.\r\n\r\n(Image source- https://lh6.ggpht.com/mp86vbELnqLi2FzvhiKdPX31_oiTRLNyeK8x4IIrbF5eD1D5RdnVwjQP0hwMNR_JdA=w300\r\n\r\nhttps://www.whatsapp.com/img/fb-post.jpg)\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone" src="https://www.whatsapp.com/img/fb-post.jpg" alt="" width="794" height="388" />', 'WhatsApp''s new hidden features', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'whatsapps-new-hidden-features', '', '', '2015-07-23 23:31:06', '2015-07-23 18:01:06', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=151', 0, 'post', '', 0),
