(194, 1, '2015-07-30 11:22:36', '2015-07-30 05:52:36', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://cdn.vrworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Windows-10-1140x641.gif" alt="" width="822" height="462" />\r\n\r\nMicrosoft yesterday released its new and final version of Windows ie "Windows 10". It is now available as a free upgrade for Windows 7/ 8/ 8.1 users in 190 countries. According to Microsoft "It is the most secured release of Windows till date". "delivered as a service and kept automatically up-to-date with innovations and security updates." It will also be available at retail stores priced at $119 (Rs. 7,500) for Windows 10 Home and $199 (Rs. 12,600) for Windows 10 Pro. Windows 10 Home users can also update to Pro version by paying $99 and get the "Pro" features.\r\n\r\nAccording to Bhaskar Pramanik (Chairman, Microsoft India) "Windows 10 is the best Windows ever. Today, Windows 10 will be available across 190 countries as a free upgrade or with new PCs and tablets. It is more personal and more productive. It''s safer and more secure. And it''s familiar and always up to date. In India, more than 1500 retail stores across the country will help consumers move up to Windows 10."\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en">\r\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en"><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Windows10?src=hash">#Windows10</a> is here! Follow the celebration around the world: <a href="http://t.co/M8C1npJBLp">http://t.co/M8C1npJBLp</a><a href="http://t.co/GMKph4P89e">pic.twitter.com/GMKph4P89e</a></p>\r\n— Windows (@Windows) <a href="https://twitter.com/Windows/status/626397519635984384">July 29, 2015</a></blockquote>\r\n(Image source- http://stateschronicle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Windows-10-Launch-Leaves-Windows-XP-Behind.jpg\r\n\r\nhttp://d.ibtimes.co.uk/en/full/1401981/windows-10-launch.jpg\r\n\r\nhttp://cdn.vrworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Windows-10-1140x641.gif)\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone" src="http://d.ibtimes.co.uk/en/full/1401981/windows-10-launch.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone" src="http://stateschronicle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Windows-10-Launch-Leaves-Windows-XP-Behind.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="450" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>', 'Windows 10 Launched', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'windows-10-launched', '', '', '2015-07-30 11:22:36', '2015-07-30 05:52:36', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=194', 0, 'post', '', 0),
