(373, 1, '2015-09-24 23:12:45', '2015-09-24 17:42:45', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://cdn.ndtv.com/tech/images/vertu_signature_touch_pure_jet_red_gold1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="600" />\r\n\r\nVertu recently launched its new smartphone "Signature Touch". It has been priced at GBP 6,500 to GBP 13,700 (Rs. 6.5 lakhs to Rs. 13.8 lakhs) and will be available for pre-order from September 28th to October 8th. It will be available in 8 variants:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Jet Calf</li>\r\n	<li>Garnet Calf</li>\r\n	<li>Grape Lizard</li>\r\n	<li>Pure Jet Lizard</li>\r\n	<li>Jet Alligator</li>\r\n	<li>Pure Navy Alligator</li>\r\n	<li>Clous de Paris Alligator</li>\r\n	<li>Pure Jet Red Gold</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIts specifications are as followings:-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Android 5.1 Lollipop</li>\r\n	<li>5.2-Inch full-HD (1080x1920 pixels) resolution display (428ppi) (Sapphire Crystal screen)</li>\r\n	<li>1.5Ghz 64-Bit octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 810 processor</li>\r\n	<li>4GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>21MP Rear camera and 2.1MP front camera</li>\r\n	<li>64GB In-built storage (Expandable upto 2TB)</li>\r\n	<li>4G LTE bands (2300Mhz and 1800Mhz), NFC, Bluetooth 4.0, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, Wi-Fi Hotspot, GPS and Micro-USB</li>\r\n	<li>3160mAh Li-ion battery</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 155x74x10.8mm and weighs 225g to 236 g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n(Image source- http://cdn.ndtv.com/tech/images/vertu_signature_touch_pure_jet_red_gold1.jpg)', 'Vertu Signature Touch', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vertu-signature-touch', '', '', '2015-09-24 23:12:45', '2015-09-24 17:42:45', '', 0, 'http://thetechlog.in/?p=373', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(374, 1, '2015-09-24 23:12:29', '2015-09-24 17:42:29', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://cdn.ndtv.com/tech/images/vertu_signature_touch_pure_jet_red_gold1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="600" />\r\n\r\nVertu recently launched its new smartphone "Signature Touch". It has been priced at GBP 6,500 to GBP 13,700 (Rs. 6.5 lakhs to Rs. 13.8 lakhs) and will be available for pre-order from September 28th to October 8th. It will be available in 8 variants:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Jet Calf</li>\r\n	<li>Garnet Calf</li>\r\n	<li>Grape Lizard</li>\r\n	<li>Pure Jet Lizard</li>\r\n	<li>Jet Alligator</li>\r\n	<li>Pure Navy Alligator</li>\r\n	<li>Clous de Paris Alligator</li>\r\n	<li>Pure Jet Red Gold</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIts specifications are as followings:-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Android 5.1 Lollipop</li>\r\n	<li>5.2-Inch full-HD (1080x1920 pixels) resolution display (428ppi) (Sapphire Crystal screen)</li>\r\n	<li>1.5Ghz 64-Bit octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 810 processor</li>\r\n	<li>4GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>21MP Rear camera and 2.1MP front camera</li>\r\n	<li>64GB In-built storage (Expandable upto 2TB)</li>\r\n	<li>4G LTE bands (2300Mhz and 1800Mhz), NFC, Bluetooth 4.0, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, Wi-Fi Hotspot, GPS and Micro-USB</li>\r\n	<li>3160mAh Li-ion battery</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 155x74x10.8mm and weighs 225g to 236 g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n(Image source- http://cdn.ndtv.com/tech/images/vertu_signature_touch_pure_jet_red_gold1.jpg)', 'Vertu Signature Touch', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '373-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-24 23:12:29', '2015-09-24 17:42:29', '', 373, 'http://thetechlog.in/2015/09/24/373-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(375, 1, '2015-10-01 08:39:53', '2015-10-01 03:09:53', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://cdn2.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_18.54.48.png?itok=qpQH9NqC" alt="" width="797" height="363" />\r\n\r\nGoogle yesterday launched its two new smartphones "LG Nexus 5X and Huawei Nexus 6P" at the Google I/O in California. They have been priced at:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Nexus 5X (Available in Carbon, Quartz and Ice colors)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rs. 31,900 (16GB Internal storage variant)</li>\r\n	<li>Rs. 35,900 (32GB Internal storage variant)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Nexus 6P (Available in Aluminum, Graphite and Frost colors)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rs. 39,999 (32GB Internal storage variant)</li>\r\n	<li>Rs. 42,999 (64GB Internal storage variant)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGoogle also launched some accessories along with their new smartphones like:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Nexus 5X Folio case priced at Rs. 3,200</li>\r\n	<li>Nexus 5X Case priced at Rs. 2,800</li>\r\n	<li>Adopted Protective Case for Nexus 5X priced at Rs. 1,800</li>\r\n	<li>Speck Candyshell Grip Case for Nexus 5X priced at Rs. 2,500</li>\r\n	<li>Nexus 6P Folio case priced at Rs. 3,900</li>\r\n	<li>Nexus 6P Case priced at Rs. 2,800</li>\r\n	<li>Adopted Protective Case for Nexus 6P priced at Rs. 1,800</li>\r\n	<li>Speck Candyshell Grip Case for Nexus 6P priced at Rs. 3,000</li>\r\n	<li>USB Type-C charger priced at Rs. 1,799</li>\r\n	<li>Type-C to Type-C cable priced at Rs. 1,399</li>\r\n	<li>Standard USB to Type-C cable priced at Rs. 909</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGoogle has also cut the price of the Nexus 6. It is now available at:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rs. 33,800 (32GB Internal storage variant)</li>\r\n	<li>Rs. 37,600 (64GB Internal storage variant)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSpecifications:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en">Introducing <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Nexus6P?src=hash">#Nexus6P</a> <a href="https://t.co/8ZUH386SNI">https://t.co