/cdn2.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_19.18.11_0.png?itok=ZO6OdkAN" alt="" width="823" height="537" />\n\n<img class="alignnone" src="http://cdn1.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_19.18.25.png?itok=8DmXhyJw" alt="" width="822" height="844" />\n\nLG Google Nexus 5X\n<ul>\n	<li> Android 6.0 Marshmallow</li>\n	<li>5.2-Inch Full HD LCD display (424 ppi) (Corning Gorilla Glass 3 and fingerprint/smudge-resistant oleophobic coating)</li>\n	<li>2GHz Hexa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 808 processor</li>\n	<li>2GB LPDDR3 RAM</li>\n	<li>12.3MP Rear camera (4K) and 5MP front camera</li>\n	<li>Adreo 418 GPU</li>\n	<li>Dimensions:147.0 x 72.6 x 7.9 mm and weighs 136g</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\nBoth devices are expected to be shipped by October.\n\n<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MQ9GDfE3BZg" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n(Image source- http://cdn2.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_18.54.48.png?itok=qpQH9NqC\n\nhttp://cdn2.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_19.13.53.png?itok=pXAaRcR8\n\nhttp://cdn2.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_19.14.04.png?itok=141v0ot3\n\nhttp://cdn2.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_19.18.11_0.png?itok=ZO6OdkAN\n\nhttp://cdn1.knowyourmobile.com/sites/knowyourmobilecom/files/styles/gallery_wide/public/2015/09/screenshot_2015-09-29_at_19.18.25.png?itok=8DmXhyJw)', 'Google Nexus 5X and Google Nexus 6P launched', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '375-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-01 18:34:31', '2015-10-01 13:04:31', '', 375, 'http://thetechlog.in/