(547, 1, '2015-12-05 12:38:37', '2015-12-05 07:08:37', '<img class="alignnone" src="http://images.frandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/galaxy-a3-a-5-a7-2016.jpg" alt="" width="769" height="430" />\r\n\r\nSamsung recently launched its 3 new smartphones in China. Their specifications are as below:-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2>Samsung Galaxy A7 2016</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Android 5.1 Lollipop</li>\r\n	<li>5.5 Inch full-HD (1080x1920 pixels)Super Amoled display</li>\r\n	<li>1.6GHz Octa-core processor</li>\r\n	<li>3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>13MP Rear camera and a 5MP front camera</li>\r\n	<li>16GB In-built storage (Expandable upto 128GB)</li>\r\n	<li>4G LTE</li>\r\n	<li>Fingerprint scanner</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 151.5x74.1x7.3mm and weighs 172g</li>\r\n	<li>3300mAh Battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2>Samsung Galaxy A5 2016 (Same specifications as A7 Except)</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.2 Inch full-HD Super Amoled display</li>\r\n	<li>2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>2900mAh Battery</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 144.8x71.0x7.3mm and weighs 155g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2>Samsung Galaxy A3 2016</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>4.7 Inch HD (720x1280 pixels)Super Amoled display</li>\r\n	<li>1.5Ghz Quad core processor</li>\r\n	<li>1.5GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>2300mAh Battery</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 134.5x65.2x7.3mm and weighs 132g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAccording to JK Shin (CEO and Head of Samsung''s IT &amp; Mobile Business),"At Samsung, we are committed to continued innovation, inspired by the feedback and needs of our wide range of consumers, with the introduction of the Galaxy A (2016), we took the consumer feedback on our original Galaxy A models and made thoughtful and impactful improvements offering consumers a seamless convergence of style and performance for their everyday lifestyles."\r\n\r\n(Image source- http://images.frandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/galaxy-a3-a-5-a7-2016.jpg)', 'Samsung Galaxy A3 (2016), Galaxy A5 (2016) and Galaxy A7 (2016)', '', 'publish', 'open'